20590 REM
20591 REM Compare measured scan to standard
20592 REM
20600 NOISE=1E+10:for i=5 to 24: print#4, i,ms(i):next
20610 FOR J=0 TO 4
20620   SUMMM=0:SUMM=0:SUMSM=0
20630   FOR I=9 TO 20
