20690   S(J)=(SUMSM-NOISE*SUMS)^2/(SUMSS*(SUMMM-2*NOISE*SUMM+12*NOISE^2))
20700   IF J=2 THEN SNR = SUMM/(12*ABS(NOISE))
20710   LOCATE JC+2+J,JR:PRINT S(J)
20720 NEXT
